text:
Asked for curry sauce on my rice, didn't put any curry sauce..
Little bits of meat on the veggie considered meat...
Pork chop is 3.5 never inform me in advance...
DO NOT COME TO THIS STALL

Very dishonest staff. Do check for overpricing.  They overcharged each time and did not honor the rice garden pricing according to the color tags for ntuc members. Even if non member, clearly is overcharging.. Felt con by the staff  -  tofu with very little meat,  2 green veg  - $5.20. When I asked to the staff serving, he sounded very loud and angry.  Please avoid this stall if possible.

Almost want to walk away not paying.
Newly opened in kopitiam. They offer a wide variety of dishes. Remember to present your ntuc card for kopitiam promotions.
Couldnâ€™t claim my CDC vouchers although there was a sign that said you could claim CDC vouchers at their stall.  Owner was very unfriendly and rude.
Food is okay but service is very poor, rude staff. Often overcharge!
